  %p
    Rubyest meetup is heavily inspired by Barcelona on Rails and London LRUG meetups. 
    Our aim is to engage people and exchange ruby technology and knowledge.

  %h2 Seminar topics
  %p
    Most meetup topics are related to ruby programming, however we welcome other topics
    as long as it is interesting for ruby people. You are welcome to make a presentation, 
    please email to 
    = link_to 'Priit', 'mailto:priit@gitnation.com'

  %h2 Who is coming
  %p
    We expect to see ruby professionals, beginners and students.

  %h2 Regular schedule
  %p
    Currently we are organizing meetups four times in year - 
     January, April, July and October. Meetup takes place 
    <b>on the second Thursday of the month starting 18:30</b>.

